This directory hosts the halon_facts.yaml files for various cluster setups.

List of halon_facts.yaml files:

1) singlenode/halon_facts.yaml
    Cluster is defined in bootstrap-cluster.sh script under `s3single` name.
    Cluster consists of one Motr node and one S3 server node. S3 server node
    is configured in halon_facts.yaml file to run two instances of s3server.
